                </div>
                <!-- RIGHT -->
                <div>
                    <div class="bridge-tap">
                        <label>
                            <input type="radio" name="bridge-tap" checked>
                            <div>
                                Portfolio
                            </div>
                        </label>
                        <label onclick="historyView()">
                            <input type="radio" name="bridge-tap">
                            <div>
                                Activity
                            </div>
                        </label>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bridge-portfolio">
                        <div class="wallet-disconnect" style="display: none;">
                            <div>
                                <p>
                                    kthulu bridge는 확장가능하며 안전한 크로스체인 통신네트워크입니다. <br />
                                    브릿지로 거래를 제출할 준비가 되면 지갑을 연결하세요.
                                </p>

                                <button>
                                    지갑연결
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bridge-active bridgeStatusChk" style="display: none">
                            <div>
                                <span class="bridge-active-end">
                                    TODAY
                                </span>

                                <div class="bridge-active-send">
                                    <div id="statusFromNetwork">
                                        <i class="token-icon"></i>
                                        Ethereum
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="statusFromAccount">
                                        0xE...901c
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <i></i>
                                <div class="bridge-active-to">
                                    <div id="statusToNetwork">
                                        <i class="token-icon"></i>
                                        Ethereum
                                    </div>
                                    <div id="statusToAccount">
                                        0xE...901c
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <p>
                                    You can check it in the activity tab after 5 minutes.
                                </p>
